
'''Marie Claire Uwumuremyi''' (wavutse 1979) ni umunyapolitiki wo mu [[Rwanda]]. Kuva mu 2018 yabaye umwe mu bagize Umutwe rw'Abadepite  mu nteko ishingamategeko y' u [[Rwanda]]. <ref name="Details">[https://www.parliament.gov.rw/index.php?id=125&width=650&detailId=425 Member details], [[Parliament of Rwanda]]. Accessed 3 May 2020.</ref>

== Ubuzima ==
Mbere yo kuba umudepite, Marie Claire Uwumuremyi yakoraga kuri Biro y'Ubutaka, nk'umukozi ushinzwe ubutaka mu Karere akaba n'ushinzwe guha agaciro ubutaka mu Karere<ref>https://www.nyanza.gov.rw/default-title-12/hatangijwe-gahunda-zo-kwibuka-ku-nshuro-ya-25-jenoside-yakorewe-abatutsi-mu-1994</ref>. <ref name="Details">[https://www.parliament.gov.rw/index.php?id=125&width=650&detailId=425 Member details], [[Parliament of Rwanda]]. Accessed 3 May 2020.</ref> Yabaye Perezida w'Inama y'Abagore (CNF) mu Ntara y'Amajyepfo . Ku munsi mpuzamahanga w’abagore bo mu cyaro 2011 yashishikarije abagore bo mu Murenge wa Tumba, mu [[Akarere ka Huye|Karere ka Huye]], gukoresha amahirwe leta itanga, no guteza imbere ubucuruzi bwabo bafata inguzanyo. <ref>[https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/35977 Huye women urged to embrace gov’t programmes], ''[[The New Times (Rwanda)|The New Times]]'', October 18, 2011. Accessed 3 May 2020.</ref>

Muri Nzeri 2018 yabaye umudepite mu [[Akarere ka Nyanza|Karere ka Nyanza]], Intara y'Amajyepfo, nk'uhagarariye abagore. <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/189017</ref><ref name="Details">[https://www.parliament.gov.rw/index.php?id=125&width=650&detailId=425 Member details], [[Parliament of Rwanda]]. Accessed 3 May 2020.</ref> Mu Kwakira 2018, yitabiriye ibirori by’umunsi w’ibiribwa ku isi, ashyigikira gahunda ya Girinka ya guverinoma y’u [[Rwanda]] (Inka imwe ku muryango ukennye). <ref>Jean de Dieu Nsabimana, [https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/girinka-programme-driving-rwandas-ambitious-target-zero-hunger Girinka programme driving Rwanda’s ambitious target of zero hunger], ''[[The New Times (Rwanda)|The New Times]]'', October 29, 2018. Accessed 3 May 2020.</ref> Ukuboza 2019 yatorewe kuba muri Komite Nyobozi y’umutwe w’Abadepite bagize Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Commonwealth (CWP). <ref>Emmanuel Ntirenganya, [https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/rwanda-chapter-commonwealth-women-mps-elect-new-committee Rwanda chapter of Commonwealth women MPs elect new committee], ''The New Times'', December 17, 2019. Accessed 3 May 2020.</ref> Muri Kamena 2019, ubwo yavugaga mu muhango wo kwibuka wabereye mu Murenge wa Mukingo, mu [[Akarere ka Nyanza|Karere ka Nyanza]], yibukije abamuteze amatwi akamaro ko kwibuka [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|jenoside yo]] mu Rwanda<ref>https://cnlg.gov.rw/index.php?id=87&L=1&tx_news_pi1%5Bnews%5D=3721&tx_news_pi1%5Bcontroller%5D=News&tx_news_pi1%5Baction%5D=detail&cHash=22b14d781b6cef50b2c7daa9e16a5096</ref>:

